# Keep secrets, VCS, and heavy/generated dirs out of the build context.
# Provider keys are mounted at runtime (-v test/provider:/secrets:ro), never baked in.
**/node_modules
.git
test/provider
keys
**/.open-next
**/.wrangler
**/.next
**/target
**/.turbo
bin
**/*.log
# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the workspace libs are built on the
# host and copied in, because a cold tsc build inside this image cannot resolve
# the @as/* workspace types reliably.
